{"lemma":"ضِغْنٌ","slug":"ضِغْنٌ","root":"ض.غ.ن","root_slug":"ض-غ-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-غ-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25881"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%90%D8%BA%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25881","headword_ar":"ضِغْنٌ","root":"Dgn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[said by some to be an inf. n.: (see 1:)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DagiynapN","text_ar":"ضَغِينَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement rancour"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enmity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"violent hatred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDogaAnN","text_ar":"اَضْغَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (MA, Msb;) and that of ↓ the latter is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DagaAy^inu","text_ar":"ضَغَايِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DagiynN","text_ar":"ضَغِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DagiynapN","text_ar":"ضَغِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather a coll. gen. n.,] or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be elided by poetic license; or these two may be dial. vars., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huq~N","text_ar":"حُقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huq~apN","text_ar":"حُقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[accord. to some], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayaADN","text_ar":"بَيَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayaADapN","text_ar":"بَيَاضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says, when he has sought to gain a person's good will, or approval,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salalotu Digona fulaAnK","text_ar":"سَلَلْتُ ضِغْنَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dagiynatahu","text_ar":"ضَغِينَتَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drew forth the rancour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And a woman who hates her husband is said to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu DigonK EalaY zawojihaA","text_ar":"ذَاتُ ضِغْنٍ عَلَى زَوْجِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who has a feeling of rancour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against her husband"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Difficulty of disposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a beast: so in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu DigonK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ ضِغْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[A beast ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAb~apN","text_ar":"دَابَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a difficult disposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) See also the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu $agobK waDigonK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ شَغْبٍ وَضِغْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a she-ass, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$gb","text_ar":"شغب"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inclination."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DigoniY A_ilaY fulaAnK","text_ar":"ضِغْنِى اـِلَى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My inclination is towards such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Desire;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yearning"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing of the soul."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN *aAtu","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ ذَاتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DigonK","text_ar":"ضِغْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel yearning towards,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing for, her home,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accustomed place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and her mates."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. [See a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifaAqN","text_ar":"رِفَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DigonN","text_ar":"ضِغْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus used, metaphorically, in relation to women. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a region, quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAHiyapN","text_ar":"نَاحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboT","text_ar":"اـِبْط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot, bottom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus correctly, as in the “ Nawádir: ” in the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljamal","text_ar":"الجَمَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljabal","text_ar":"الجَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","MA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}